<div class="row mb-5">
  <div class="col" align="center">
    <p>ComfyDNS gives you a fully-standards-compliant DNS server with a modern web UI. 
    It doesn't make any assumptions about how much you know about DNS 
    (unlike B.I.N.D. and other "old school" implementations). Pull a docker image, run the container,
    and visit the web UI. It's that easy.</p>
  </div>
</div>

